{"tid":2218495,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"藍韜文：拘黃之鋒證港針對異見","createTime":"2020-09-26T08:59:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-26T08:59:52.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"43140095b3e87c37d9423fc61b27adaeeff8ac8f","tid":2218495,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T08:59:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200926/6OZCQJ3ZGZGLHDXC5VOCLRFVTQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200926%2F6OZCQJ3ZGZGLHDXC5VOCLRFVTQ%2F&d=I0uz%2BNPXkLchxl3mN3HTu9XdGXproJJDEW77mXnEmng%3D&h=718dec43\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200926%2F6OZCQJ3ZGZGLHDXC5VOCLRFVTQ%2F&h=c44b1b0b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200926/6OZCQJ3ZGZGLHDXC5VOCLRFVTQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n藍韜文：拘黃之鋒證港針對異見<br />\n<br />\n前香港眾志秘書長黃之鋒前日因為一年前的集會再次被拘捕，警方指他涉嫌於去年10月參與未經批准集結及違反《蒙面法》，事件引起國際關注。英國外相藍韜文（Dominic Raab）在Twitter發文表示「深切關注黃之鋒被捕，這是香港當局針對異見人士的又一例子，中港兩地政府必須尊重港人的自由和權利，那是受到《中英聯合聲明》保障。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/r_SdLgUZ7xafqEr4AbOyIhnY17s=/1342x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YPD26ACZ5FBLFDCPMPQVULDEDM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fr_SdLgUZ7xafqEr4AbOyIhnY17s%3D%2F1342x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYPD26ACZ5FBLFDCPMPQVULDEDM.jpg&h=cc1510e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■黃之鋒前日到中區警署報到時再被拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n英副外相促中國維護《聯合聲明》<br />\n<br />\n英國外交部次官艾哈邁德（Tariq Ahmad）昨日向聯合國人權理事會發表演說，批評中國在香港實施國安法，試圖以酷刑鏟除異己。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n另外，美國聯邦參議員魯比奧（Marco Rubio）加入聲援黃之鋒行列，他在Twitter發文指「中國下令香港警察逮捕黃之鋒，理由是因為他戴口罩」，批評「中共持續打壓持不同意見的人士」。另一位聯邦參議員布萊克本（Marsha Blackburn）也指「黃之鋒是自由鬥士」，警告「今日香港，明日台灣」，她呼籲國際社會不要再被習近平的甜言蜜語蒙騙。<br />\n<br />\n路透社/ 中央社"}]}